snippet.textDisplay: Messi has always had that vision in front of the goal. Now that hes getting older, he cant run as much as he used too. That's why I think he need to be a fixed forward. Messi now needs someone who can give him those passes, and this team has the players adequate enough for this this tactic, but, these players, I feel like they're too dependent on Messi, simply because the image of Barcelona has been Messi for the last few years. This team now needs Messi to be just like  any other player. Ronaldo has taken advantage that his teammates make the plays, and all he has to do  is finish. That why hes been successful at Juventus. Barcelona as as a whole, needs to accept that Messi isnt the same and will never be the same but yet he has soo much too give for Barcelona.
